Description:
"My Wallaper Gallery" This is a very handy application to change your wallpaper on your desktop.
You can easely browse thru the categories and in one click your wallpaper is changed in what you want.

Beta testers wanted.

Installation instructions:
1. Execute the mwg_0.1_beta_setup.exe file.
2. Follow installation instructions.
3. Run the program from where you installed.
3. Enjoy the program.
